task.description:
Create tests/unit/dashboard/test_service_adapters.py:

class TestAdapterBase:
  - test_adapter_has_connect_method() — all adapters inherit ServiceAdapter ABC
  - test_adapter_has_query_method() — query(endpoint, params) -> dict
  - test_adapter_cache_ttl_respected() — second call within TTL returns cached result
  - test_adapter_returns_empty_on_unavailable() — connection error → {} not exception
  - test_adapter_status_reports_healthy_unhealthy() — status() returns {"healthy": bool}

class TestMLflowAdapter:
  - test_mlflow_adapter_queries_experiments() — mock httpx, GET /api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/list
  - test_mlflow_adapter_queries_runs() — mock httpx, GET /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/search
  - test_mlflow_adapter_formats_metrics() — returns {"runs": [...], "n_experiments": int}
  - test_mlflow_adapter_url_from_env() — reads MLFLOW_TRACKING_URI (Rule #22)

class TestPrefectAdapter:
  - test_prefect_adapter_queries_flow_runs() — mock httpx, GET /api/flow_runs
  - test_prefect_adapter_formats_status() — returns {"active_runs": int, "recent": [...]}

class TestBentoMLAdapter:
  - test_bentoml_adapter_queries_models() — mock httpx, GET /metrics (or /docs)
  - test_bentoml_adapter_formats_serving_info() — returns {"endpoints": [...], "latency_ms": float}

Create deployment/docker/Dockerfile.dashboard-ui: FROM node:20-alpine AS builder WORKDIR /app COPY frontend/package*.json ./ RUN npm ci COPY frontend/ . ARG VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8090 RUN npm run build
FROM nginx:alpine COPY --from=builder /app/dist /usr/share/nginx/html COPY deployment/nginx/dashboard.conf /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf EXPOSE ${DASHBOARD_UI_PORT:-3002}
Note: VITE_API_URL is a build-time env var (Vite bakes it in at build). For development: vite dev proxy to API at localhost:8090.

Create tests/integration/dashboard/test_dashboard_smoke.py:

@pytest.mark.requires_docker
@pytest.mark.slow
class TestDashboardSmoke:
  - test_dashboard_api_health_endpoint() — GET http://localhost:8090/api/health returns 200
  - test_dashboard_api_mlflow_endpoint() — GET /api/mlflow/experiments returns 200
  - test_dashboard_api_prefect_endpoint() — GET /api/prefect/flows returns 200
  - test_dashboard_ui_serves_html() — GET http://localhost:3002 returns 200 HTML

@pytest.mark.slow
class TestDashboardAPIUnit:
  - test_all_routers_importable() — import all router modules without error
  - test_fastapi_app_starts() — TestClient(app).get("/health") returns 200
  - test_adapters_all_instantiable() — all adapter classes construct without error
  - test_health_endpoint_returns_schema() — /api/health response has "overall", "alerts" keys
